# @summary:      A Forensic Integrity Ledger for immutable proof of intent. 
#                Cryptographically signs raw incoming mutation pleas (HMAC-SHA256) 
#                and asynchronously inscripts them into an append-only JSONL 
#                chronicle before restoring the byte-stream for execution.
# @vibe:         [security, forensics, hmac, audit-log, non-repudiation, immutable]
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# @provides:     [capability:intent-notarization, capability:forensic-audit-trail, capability:request-signing]
